snippet.title: RGO: Rogue Trooper PC HD Gameplay
snippet.description:
Rogue Trooper played at 1080p.

Computer Specs:
OS: Windows 8.1 Pro 64bit
MB: Asus Z87-A
CPU: Intel Core i7-4770
GPU: Gigabyte GTX 770 OC
RAM: AData XPG V2 2x4GB 1600MHz

Intro song: "IDY" by URB
Outro song: "UP" by Astmatic Astronaut
Both song can be found on freemusicarchive.org

Can be purchased here:
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/7020/

GOG: http://www.gog.com/game/rogue_trooper
